{"tid":1463181,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"每日下午到徬晚呢個鐘數就會有班人屌","createTime":"2019-08-13T12:19:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T12:53:32.000Z","uid":118688,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d839923d46d99969d6728203e87a3c3f3b5f40cd","tid":1463181,"uid":118688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T12:19:25.000Z","msg":"明明現場得兩個地方阻緊旅客 有咩係現場講<br />\n上連登講比邊撚個聽？ 現場嘅人忙緊塞住<br />\n係屋企個班就係到揾嘢屌 唔係第一日架啦<br />\nd人返到嚟就靜返晒 每日如是<br />\nd割唔割post問嚟多閪餘<br />\n宜家係因為唔撚夠人 <br />\n不論文宣定冇出嚟嘅 都做得好唔夠<br />\n先會有被逼少人去塞departure出現<br />\n點解少人仲要塞<br />\n因為單日計嘅損失只係幾千萬 <br />\n但連續做 影響嘅唔只係客貨運<br />\n係香港既外資企業<br />\n雪球要滾到咁撚大<br />\n政府先要跪低<br />\n呢一刻仲比d互屌post上嚟嘅<br />\n你自己醒啦"},{"pid":"e8682043461cf8dc40d2fd9984941f4562af8ef2","tid":1463181,"uid":118688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T12:21:44.000Z","msg":"推啦 咪撚再推d垃圾互屌文<br />\n諗點樣補救 一齊進步個班先係大家要思考既嘢<br />\n大台指控示威者好反感<br />\n唔好比自己變大台"},{"pid":"ae1a0abef31c33002a16e954b62a54e101b11584","tid":1463181,"uid":118688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T12:22:22.000Z","msg":"721 811"},{"pid":"037b2fd9fa3885cc5ca6460f97abe57e0e30316a","tid":1463181,"uid":118688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T12:23:45.000Z","msg":"721 811"},{"pid":"8e3dfe3e70d7d3ea8ba7bb7f96df09d7cba5d26b","tid":1463181,"uid":285854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T12:23:54.000Z","msg":"但p牌已經一日一post架啦，大家唔好正係話三毛五毛，要獨立思考"},{"pid":"86c11cdcbe1d05247c0bf6ebbaa24e4ad76cebac","tid":1463181,"uid":270871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T12:23:55.000Z","msg":"同意"},{"pid":"1c1e29a4714a0610e6047df4bbe3a78f1670ec89","tid":1463181,"uid":118688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T12:24:57.000Z","msg":"721 811"},{"pid":"f629bb8677f92e8406b427c269aa2341f5b25dc5","tid":1463181,"uid":6275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T12:25:01.00